	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>You might take a peek at getting to High Hold pass.&nbsp;&nbsp;You shouldn't have any trouble getting there from level 4 on (I've been throught there many times as a 4 to 8 player).  The key to traveling at your level is to always have invisibility on and NEVER go into Kithicor Forrest at night!  (Unless you don't mind corpse retrieval)  Always keep an eye on your messages, if you see, you feel yourself starting to appear.  Take stock of your surroundings, if there are no monsters, cast invis immediately.  If there are move away from them (even if that's backwards) and cast again.  Staying near the zone edge is usually safest (although I only do that in Kithicor Forrest).  There's a vendor in High Hold Keep with all your 8+ pets.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
