ause I am totaly paranoid and dont want to lose exp.<br><br>But I know that there is a lot of good info that I could learn from you senior players, and I will respect and honor all that are willing to help me learn how to play properly, and contribute to my fellow players.<br><br>My level 12 Enchanters name is Zoidicus <br>My level 20 Magcians name is Revolt<br>I play on the Rathe server, and I would like to be an apprentice to who ever needs one.<br><br>Please send me your suggestions on spell combonations, strategies and techniques.<br><br>Enchanters Rock.<br><br>Please help.<br><br>Thank you.<br>May safe journeys, and heavy loot come your way.<br><br>Zoidicus.<br><br><br><br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
