 in the fashion that is specified above.<br><br>Once you recieve the Bartenders compendium, make your way to Oggok using the directions and Loc chart provided.<br>I would suggest making an Ogre player so you can map out the city.<br>Only go in with Dark Elf ilusion, and always cast aliance on Clurg the Ogre.<br><br>Once you do this and give him the Bartenders Compendium you will recieve a Stein of Moggok.<br><br>Gate back to FP, and get another TP to NK, to start the quest again.<br><br>If you are on the Rathe Server, send me a tell.<br>I would be happy to escort for new questers.<br><br>My players are:<br>Revolt (Magician) Guardians of the Faith<br>Zoidicus (Enchanter) Guardians of the Faith<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>   <br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
